function flip(e) {
  current = e.style.display;
  if (current == 'block') {
    e.style.display = 'none';
    return 0;
  }
  else {
    e.style.display = 'block';
    return 1;

{
  var res = -1;  if (document.getElementById) {

  }

    // this is the way old msie versions work

  if(elem) {

  }

}
